    <lb n="2"/><unclear>y</unclear> saṁnvata duka kamrateṅa jagat ta vraḥ ku<unclear>ṭ</unclear>i
</p></div>
<div type="textpart" subtype="face" n="C">
    <p>
    <lb n="3"/>jā vraḥ rājadharmma</p>
</div>
